\f3\b0 \cf0 Use Pester to set alarms for times in the future. Alarms that are scheduled to expire after you quit Pester are saved automatically. Pester must be running in order to notify you that an alarm has expired. If an alarm expires while Pester isn\'d5t running, you will not be notified, but the alarm\'d5s time will be \'d2\'c7expired\'c8\'d3 in Pester\'d5s alarm list.\
